        <item>
            <title>跑马地马场引入 AI 数据赛马分析   The Beat 与 Vantage 设施开幕</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/21/the-beat-vantage/hottopic/walk/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=the-beat-vantage</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/21/the-beat-vantage/hottopic/walk/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 14:00:13 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩乐好去处]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[The Beat]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Vantage]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[跑马地]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[香港赛马会]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1276534</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">香港赛马会于跑马地马场全新推出 The Beat 和 Vantage，以数码化设计满足年轻一代马迷的需求。The Beat 和 Vantage 结合了高级餐饮娱乐元素、人工智能（AI）及大数据技术，让顾客在竞赛研究和体验上焕然一新。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1276535 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241121at-5-694x455.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="455" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241121at-5-694x455.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241121at-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲香港赛马会于跑马地马场全新推出 The Beat 和 Vantage（图片来源：<a href="https://racingnews.hkjc.com/chinese/2024/11/20/the-beat%E5%8F%8Avantage%E6%8A%8A%E5%B6%84%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84ai%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E8%B3%BD%E9%A6%AC%E9%AB%94%E9%A9%97%E5%B8%B6%E5%88%B0%E8%B7%91%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%A6%AC%E5%A0%B4/">香港赛马会</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">香港赛马会客户策略、体验及创新事务执行总监侯德洋透露，从构想到设施落成，整个过程历时一年。马会计划对顾客旅程进行全面数码化升级，涵盖赛前准备、赛马日体验及赛后参与，逐步将革新扩展至沙田马场等其他场所，带来更丰富的观赛体验。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">新设施的重点之一是位于跑马地联合看台二楼的 The Beat 互动式 AI 拣马站，The Beat 以其巨型 LED 幕墙为特色，结合大数据及 AI 技术，让马迷能够输入赛驹状态、档位、骑师表现、练马师及途程等多个参数，即时获得心水马匹的胜算比较。即使对赛马运动不熟悉的新手，亦可以借此工具快速上手。侯德洋形容体验有如「打游戏」，简单易用又趣味盎然，让参与者更轻松地投入其中。选定心水马匹后，宾客可透过马会手机应用程式直接下注，无需翻查繁琐的马经数据。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1276536 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241121at-6-694x454.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="454" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241121at-6-694x454.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241121at-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲跑马地联合看台二楼的 The Beat 互动式 AI 拣马站（图片来源：<a href="https://racingnews.hkjc.com/chinese/2024/11/20/the-beat%E5%8F%8Avantage%E6%8A%8A%E5%B6%84%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84ai%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E8%B3%BD%E9%A6%AC%E9%AB%94%E9%A9%97%E5%B8%B6%E5%88%B0%E8%B7%91%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%A6%AC%E5%A0%B4/">香港赛马会</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1276537 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241121at-7-694x456.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="456" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241121at-7-694x456.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241121at-7.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1276538 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241121at-8-694x453.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="453" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241121at-8-694x453.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241121at-8.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲The Beat 有巨型 LED 幕墙，结合大数据及 AI 技术，马迷能够输入赛驹状态、档位等资料（图片来源：<a href="https://racingnews.hkjc.com/chinese/2024/11/20/the-beat%E5%8F%8Avantage%E6%8A%8A%E5%B6%84%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84ai%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E8%B3%BD%E9%A6%AC%E9%AB%94%E9%A9%97%E5%B8%B6%E5%88%B0%E8%B7%91%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%A6%AC%E5%A0%B4/">香港赛马会</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">而位于三楼的 Vantage 则主打高级餐饮及沉浸式体验，提供全景落地玻璃视野，顾客可在此观赏赛马实况，同时享用精致菜肴、招牌鸡尾酒及手工啤酒。设施亦融入了音乐元素，The Beat 的现场乐队表演及 Vantage 的顶尖唱片骑师轮流登场。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1276539 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241121at-9-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241121at-9-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241121at-9.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲三楼的 Vantage 则主打高级餐饮及沉浸式体验（图片来源：<a href="https://racingnews.hkjc.com/chinese/2024/11/20/the-beat%E5%8F%8Avantage%E6%8A%8A%E5%B6%84%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84ai%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E8%B3%BD%E9%A6%AC%E9%AB%94%E9%A9%97%E5%B8%B6%E5%88%B0%E8%B7%91%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%A6%AC%E5%A0%B4/">香港赛马会</a>）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1276540 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241121at-10-694x460.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="460" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241121at-10-694x460.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241121at-10.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1276541 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241121at-11-694x460.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="460" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241121at-11-694x460.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241121at-11.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲顾客可在此观赏赛马实况，同时享用精致菜肴、招牌鸡尾酒及手工啤酒（图片来源：<a href="https://racingnews.hkjc.com/chinese/2024/11/20/the-beat%E5%8F%8Avantage%E6%8A%8A%E5%B6%84%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84ai%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E8%B3%BD%E9%A6%AC%E9%AB%94%E9%A9%97%E5%B8%B6%E5%88%B0%E8%B7%91%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%A6%AC%E5%A0%B4/">香港赛马会</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">赛马会行政总裁应家柏强调，要维持香港作为国际品牌的世界级赛马地位，必须紧贴数码时代的顾客需求。沙田马场及跑马地啤酒园亦将引入类似数码设施，如数码马匹亮相圈等，进一步扩展数码赛马体验的触角。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">沙田彭福公园将于 2026 年开放，届时将加入以小马为主题的体验区，吸引家庭和年轻一代参与，从小培养对赛马运动的兴趣，延续赛马文化。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://racingnews.hkjc.com/chinese/2024/11/20/the-beat%E5%8F%8Avantage%E6%8A%8A%E5%B6%84%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84ai%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E8%B3%BD%E9%A6%AC%E9%AB%94%E9%A9%97%E5%B8%B6%E5%88%B0%E8%B7%91%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%A6%AC%E5%A0%B4/">香港赛马会</a>、<a href="https://www.am730.com.hk/%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0/%E8%B7%91%E9%A6%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%A6%AC%E5%A0%B4%E6%8E%A8%E9%A4%90%E9%A3%B2-%E8%B3%BD%E9%A6%AC-%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%94%E9%A9%97-%E4%BA%92%E5%8B%95ai%E6%8F%80%E9%A6%AC%E7%AB%99%E7%94%A8ai%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%8B%9D%E7%8E%87/508762">AM730</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/11/21/the-beat-vantage/hottopic/walk/">跑马地马场引入 AI 数据赛马分析   The Beat 与 Vantage 设施开幕</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
